en_675389_0	An initiative for enhancement of knowledge on English language and its usage was taken by the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi (SFHQ-KLN) on the instructions of Major General Niyshshanka Ranawana, Commander, Security Forces - Kilinochchi (SF-KLN) a few months ago after the SFHQ-KLN closely identified this requirement among officers.
en_675389_1	Accordingly, Major General Vijitha Ravipriya, General Officer Commanding (GOC), 57 Division who was also the former Director General Training was entrusted the task of organizing these courses.
en_675389_2	The first phase of the course commenced on August 17 and the second phase continued from August 27 - 31 under the tutelage of Mrs Manoranjani Manoharan, a well-known English Instructor in Kilinochchi area.
en_675389_3	SFHQ-KLN expects to continue the arrangement in future too.
